  "texts": [
    "However, the mixed approach of training on phonemes and graphemes [19] introduced unpleasant artifacts.FastPitch has been trained on 8× NVIDIA V100 GPUs with 32 examples per GPU and automatic mixed precision [20].",
    "The training converges after 2 hours, and full training takes 5.5 hours.",
    "We use the LAMB optimizer [21] with learning rate 0.1, β 1 = 0.9, β 2 = 0.98, and = 1e-9.Learning rate is increased during 1000 warmup steps, and then decayed according to the Transformer schedule [22].",
    "We apply weight decay of 1e-6.",
    "EvaluationWe have compared our FastPitch model with Tacotron 2 (Table 1)."
